{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":1070,"text":"I'd like to talk to you today\nabout the scale of the scientific effort"},{"time":4420,"text":"that goes into making the headlines\nyou see in the paper."},{"time":7124,"text":"Headlines that look like this\nwhen they have to do with climate change;"},{"time":10497,"text":"and like this when they have to do\nwith air quality or smog."},{"time":13367,"text":"They're two branches of the same field\nof atmospheric science."}]},{"cues":[{"time":16331,"text":"Recently, the headlines looked like this"},{"time":18287,"text":"when the Intergovernmental Panel\non Climate Change, or IPCC,"},{"time":21153,"text":"put out their report"},{"time":22328,"text":"on the state of understanding\nof the atmospheric system."},{"time":24989,"text":"That report was written\nby 620 scientists from 40 countries."},{"time":27994,"text":"They wrote almost\n1,000 pages on the topic,"},{"time":30519,"text":"and all of those pages were reviewed"},{"time":32287,"text":"by another 400-plus\nscientists and reviewers"},{"time":34438,"text":"from 113 countries."},{"time":36156,"text":"It's a big community;"},{"time":37446,"text":"such a big community, in fact,"},{"time":38928,"text":"that our annual gathering is the largest\nscientific meeting in the world."}]},{"cues":[{"time":42407,"text":"Over 15,000 scientists go\nto San Francisco every year for that."},{"time":45385,"text":"Every one of those scientists\nis in a research group,"},{"time":48016,"text":"and every research group studies\na wide variety of topics."},{"time":50769,"text":"For us at Cambridge, it's as varied\nas the El Ni√±o Oscillation,"},{"time":53767,"text":"which affects weather and climate,"},{"time":55455,"text":"to the assimilation of satellite data,"},{"time":57311,"text":"to emissions from crops that produce\nbiofuels, which is what I study."}]},{"cues":[{"time":60594,"text":"And in each one of these research areas,\nof which there are even more,"},{"time":63936,"text":"there are PhD students, like me,\nand we study incredibly narrow topics,"},{"time":67320,"text":"things as narrow as a few processes\nor a few molecules."},{"time":69941,"text":"And one of the molecules I study\nis called isoprene, which is here."},{"time":73179,"text":"It's a small organic molecule."},{"time":74850,"text":"You've probably never heard of it."},{"time":76518,"text":"The weight of a paper clip\nis approximately equal"},{"time":78944,"text":"to 900 zeta-illion -- 10 to the 21st --\nmolecules of isoprene."}]},{"cues":[{"time":82599,"text":"But despite its very small weight,"},{"time":84722,"text":"enough of it is emitted\ninto the atmosphere every year"},{"time":87302,"text":"to equal the weight\nof all the people on the planet."},{"time":89802,"text":"It's a huge amount of stuff.\nIt's equal to the weight of methane."},{"time":92883,"text":"And because it's so much stuff,"},{"time":94388,"text":"it's really important\nfor the atmospheric system."}]},{"cues":[{"time":96726,"text":"Because it's important\nto the atmospheric system,"},{"time":99046,"text":"we go to all lengths to study this thing."},{"time":101027,"text":"We blow it up and look at the pieces."},{"time":102822,"text":"This is the EUPHORE Smog Chamber in Spain."},{"time":104854,"text":"Atmospheric explosions,\nor full combustion,"},{"time":106902,"text":"takes about 15,000 times longer\nthan what happens in your car."},{"time":109836,"text":"But still, we look at the pieces."}]},{"cues":[{"time":111440,"text":"We run enormous models on supercomputers;\nthis is what I happen to do."},{"time":114809,"text":"Our models have hundreds\nof thousands of grid boxes"},{"time":117328,"text":"calculating hundreds of variables\neach, on minute timescales."},{"time":120359,"text":"It takes weeks to perform\nour integrations,"},{"time":122439,"text":"and we perform dozens of integrations\nin order to understand what's happening."}]},{"cues":[{"time":126177,"text":"We also fly all over the world\nlooking for this thing."},{"time":128970,"text":"I recently joined a field campaign\nin Malaysia -- there are others."},{"time":132175,"text":"We found a global atmospheric\nwatchtower there"},{"time":134398,"text":"in the middle of the rainforest,"},{"time":135976,"text":"and hung hundreds of thousands\nof dollars' worth of scientific equipment"},{"time":139403,"text":"off this tower,"},{"time":140578,"text":"to look for isoprene and other things\nwhile we were there."},{"time":143368,"text":"This is the tower in the middle\nof the rainforest from above,"},{"time":146267,"text":"and the tower from below."}]},{"cues":[{"time":147491,"text":"On part of that field campaign\nwe even brought an aircraft with us."},{"time":150706,"text":"And this plane, the model BAe-146,\nwhich was run by FAAM,"},{"time":153397,"text":"normally flies 120 to 130 people,"},{"time":155465,"text":"so maybe you took a similar aircraft\nto get here today."},{"time":158074,"text":"But we didn't just fly it."},{"time":159350,"text":"We were flying at 100 meters\nabove the top of the canopy"},{"time":162067,"text":"to measure this molecule --\nincredibly dangerous stuff."}]},{"cues":[{"time":164714,"text":"We have to fly at a special incline\nto make the measurements;"},{"time":167631,"text":"we hire military and test pilots\nto do the maneuvering;"},{"time":170246,"text":"we need special flight clearance."},{"time":171874,"text":"As you come around the banks\nin these valleys,"},{"time":174051,"text":"the forces can get up to two Gs;"},{"time":175611,"text":"the scientists must be\ncompletely harnessed in"},{"time":177795,"text":"in order to make measurements\nwhile on board."},{"time":179918,"text":"So as you can imagine,"},{"time":181096,"text":"the inside of the aircraft doesn't look\nlike one you'd take on vacation."},{"time":184527,"text":"It's a flying laboratory we took\nto make measurements of this molecule."}]},{"cues":[{"time":188097,"text":"We do all this to understand\nthe chemistry of one molecule."},{"time":191207,"text":"And when one student like me\nhas some sort of inclination"},{"time":193915,"text":"or understanding about that molecule,"},{"time":195740,"text":"they write one scientific paper\non the subject."},{"time":197981,"text":"And out of that field campaign\nwe'll probably get a few dozen papers"},{"time":201225,"text":"on a few dozen processes or molecules."}]},{"cues":[{"time":203086,"text":"As a body of knowledge builds up,\nit will form one subsection,"},{"time":206056,"text":"or one sub-subsection,"},{"time":207231,"text":"of an assessment like the IPCC,\nalthough we have others."},{"time":210545,"text":"And each one of the 11 chapters\nof the IPCC has six to ten subsections."},{"time":215505,"text":"So you can imagine\nthe scale of the effort."},{"time":217569,"text":"In each one of the assessments we write,\nwe always tag on a summary,"},{"time":221256,"text":"and the summary is written\nfor a non-scientific audience."},{"time":223962,"text":"And we hand that summary\nto journalists and policy makers"},{"time":226726,"text":"in order to make headlines like these."}]},{"cues":[{"time":229463,"text":"Thank you very much."}]},{"cues":[{"time":230675,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}